    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >In <strong><i>Whiskerwood Vale</i></strong> you play as <strong>Renard</strong>, a fox knight wielding a magic greatsword. On your quest to rescue the small folk of <strong><i>Whiskerwood Vale</i></strong>, you'll traverse 4 unique kingdoms that have been overrun by covetous vermin warlords seeking to expand their territory. With the help of <strong>Renard's</strong> magic sword, you will soar through the skies and explore the treacherous floating islands that are scattered throughout the world. Don't forget to collect acorns along the way to trade in at the squirrel shop for accessories, skins. and more! </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3179740/extras/d62b6b466b2680b01d1b0cfc6b0637f2.poster.avif?t=1742244814\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3179740/extras/d62b6b466b2680b01d1b0cfc6b0637f2.webm?t=1742244814\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3179740/extras/d62b6b466b2680b01d1b0cfc6b0637f2.mp4?t=1742244814\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
